- VSCode Version:
![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/3082812/21341374/45fe62f8-c69d-11e6-85ba-c91e5e5964e1.png)

- OS Version: win7 pro

Steps to Reproduce:

1. Open HTML file;
2. Press `Ctrl+Shift+V`;
3. Press `Ctrl+\`;
4. Close preview in 1st panel, what would happen as in the screenshot;
![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/3082812/21341512/eab9b658-c69d-11e6-8200-571b5b50db5a.png)

5. Change HTML file in 1st panel;
6. Preview is not updated.

PS:
1. If I don't used splitted code editor, then this scenario is work;
2. And this scenario working on a Linux for embed in html scripts and styles: https://github.com/Microsoft/vscode/issues/16081
